{"tid":2081784,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"身價大不同！達人揭「AV女優薪水等級」…她竟比OL還少","createTime":"2020-06-27T13:22:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T00:52:18.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a415260408e3f3bf9db9d124707807d204b6a367","tid":2081784,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T13:22:49.000Z","msg":"日本AV產業發展蓬勃，三上悠亞曾透露第一部AV的片酬就足以讓她在東京市中心買豪宅，也讓不少年輕女孩前仆後繼地投入暗黑界，而到底AV女優是不是很賺呢？AV達人「一劍浣春秋」也為大家揭密。<br />\n<br />\n一劍浣春秋舉例，像是永瀨未萌上節目時曾說拍完出道作收到300萬日幣（約84萬台幣），水川蓳一個月拍了10支作品進帳200萬日幣（約56萬台幣），寶生莉莉則是最慘，被公司抽成後只剩下8000日幣（約台幣2250台幣），可說是差距相當大。一劍浣春秋表示如果等級是到片商願意簽去當專屬女優的高手們，一個月只要拍1支作品，就能夠拿到80~120萬日幣（約21萬~33萬台幣），如果是遊走在各個片商拍片的企劃女優則大約是20~30萬日幣（5.6萬~8.4萬台幣）。當然片商也會看人氣和買氣片商稍微做一些調整，不這樣做的話是無法吸引到那些搶手的女優到自家拍片或是跳槽。<br />\n<br />\n至於專屬女優最多片商願意開多少呢？一劍浣春秋也大方透露「500萬日幣以上（約140萬台幣）」，不過他說要拿到這種等級薪水的女優，以一片售價3000日幣來算的話，每支作品至少要有2000片的銷量才有辦法打平，對很多女優來說其實相當不容易，所以能拿到這片酬的業界精英當然也是屈指可數，還提到之前片商Muteki為了讓女藝人下海甚至會開到600萬日幣的片酬。"},{"pid":"488207aad5554cf34777aeb56649065c745db7d3","tid":2081784,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T13:23:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/06/26/2629118-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F06%2F26%2F2629118-XXL.jpg&h=82e54156&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲三上悠亞。（圖／翻攝自推特）"},{"pid":"e82878a79731977b32d3d020648f6bd1d3680746","tid":2081784,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T13:23:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/06/26/2629121-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F06%2F26%2F2629121-XXL.jpg&h=a2861709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲永瀨未萌。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/06/26/2629120-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F06%2F26%2F2629120-XXL.jpg&h=39235b66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲水川蓳。（圖／翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/06/26/2629128-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F06%2F26%2F2629128-XXL.jpg&h=3f2f2d98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲寶生莉莉。（圖／翻攝自推特）"},{"pid":"b56b367f6a696a6fee301898f55c2c32c4c6d22e","tid":2081784,"uid":38904,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T13:25:16.000Z","msg":"依啲嘢同樣成正比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d1dff08b8c3ae67a66159a4e5fec858d604218","tid":2081784,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T13:26:19.000Z","msg":"寶生莉莉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df958041d04aefe5babc189908eafe90155251c","tid":2081784,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b56b367f6a696a6fee301898f55c2c32c4c6d22e","tid":2081784,"uid":38904,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T13:25:16.000Z","msg":"依啲嘢同樣成正比<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T13:28:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EbAkSH8VcAA64W8?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEbAkSH8VcAA64W8%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=b0e2442b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EbAkSH8UcAAXf7f?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEbAkSH8UcAAXf7f%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=1b679fda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n寶生莉莉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f62a65e48d7de113ac1be2e53766